      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……何かあったの？",
      "startTime": 6.6278459867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "葵に仕事の話がきてな\n今までと毛色が違うから、まずは相談しないとと思って",
      "startTime": 11.7000008345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "君は僕達のマネージャーなんだから\nいちいち僕に相談しないで、OKしても良かったのに",
      "startTime": 18.7633798521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、一体{user}君が\n悩むほどの仕事ってなんなの？",
      "startTime": 24.3967133126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、前にすずがドラマにゲスト出演しただろう？\n毎週、殺人事件を解決していく……",
      "startTime": 31.5333332778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、あれ。僕も観たよ\n今度は僕に、あのドラマへの出演依頼がきたの？",
      "startTime": 38.2214063169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、僕は一体何をすればいいんだい\n死体役？　スキップしながら包丁振り回すとか？",
      "startTime": 45.7547381243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……結構やる気だな\nダンス以外の仕事は嫌がるかと思ってたんだが",
      "startTime": 52.1999968927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワの躍進のためにはなんでもやると言ったからね\n演技は未経験だけど、頑張ってみるよ",
      "startTime": 60.0627421459,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
